          <p class="text-sm mb-3">"Your goal: get hired, get stocked, get press. Website showcases designs, process, brand story. No checkout neededâ€”visitors contact for inquiries or wholesale. Best platforms: Squarespace (fashion templates), Framer (design quality), Webflow (custom portfolio). These platforms excel at visual presentation, gallery layouts, editorial aesthetics. Focus on: high-res images, garment details, fabric swatches, size specs, press features, contact form for buyers/employers.</p>
