        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-rose-600 p-5">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-3 text-rose-900">HIGH-RESOLUTION IMAGERY</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">"Fashion websites require professional photography. Smartphone photos insufficient. Budget $500-2000 for professional shoot: 20-40 garments on models, lifestyle shots, detail shots (fabric, stitching, hardware). Image quality reflects brand qualityâ€”blurry photos = cheap brand perception. Squarespace and Webflow handle high-res images beautifully with lazy loading and optimization. Upload at 2500px width minimum, let platform resize for display. Include multiple angles per garment: front, back, side, detail shot."</p>
