          <p class="text-sm mb-3">"Lookbooks should feel like fashion magazine spreads, not product grids. Mix full-bleed hero images with detail shots. Create editorial spreads: 3-5 garments styled together, telling collection story. Use white space generouslyâ€”fashion needs breathing room. Squarespace's gallery layouts designed for editorial presentation: masonry grids, horizontal scrolling, slideshow galleries. Webflow allows completely custom editorial layoutsâ€”design like magazine, not store. Editorial presentation signals premium brand justifies premium pricing."</p>
