          <p class="text-sm mb-3">"Customers want to see garments from all angles. Include 360-degree rotating views or multiple angles per garment. Webflow supports 360-degree image uploadsâ€”customers drag to rotate garment. Squarespace requires image stacks (multiple images showing different angles). This feature critical for online fashion salesâ€”reduces returns by managing expectations. Customers see garment from front, back, side, detail. Returns kill fashion e-commerce (20-30% return rates normal). 360 views reduce returns by giving complete picture before purchase.</p>
