          <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-3 text-rose-900">FABRIC & DETAIL SHOTS</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">"Fashion buyers examine details: stitching quality, fabric texture, hardware (zippers, buttons), lining. Include detail shots in lookbook: close-up of seam finishes, fabric weave, button quality. These details signal craftsmanship justifying price. Fast fashion won't show detail shotsâ€”hides poor construction. Premium brands flaunt details because quality is selling point. Squarespace's lightbox feature perfect for detail shotsâ€”click to enlarge, pinch to zoom on mobile. Let customers inspect garment virtually like they would in boutique.</p>
